			<div><strong>Patch Notes - 06/15/2004</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div><a href="http://www.worldofwarcraft.com/patchnotes/patch-6-12-04.shtml" target="_blank">http://www.worldofwarcraft.com/patch...-6-12-04.shtml</a></div>
